<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Hangar 13 Services</title>

<style>

:root{
    --gold:#d4af37;
    --dark:#050505;
    --steel:#1b1b1b;
    --text:#f5f5f5;
}


*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}


body{

    background:
    linear-gradient(
        rgba(0,0,0,.75),
        rgba(0,0,0,.95)
    ),
    url("images/hangar.jpg");

    background-size:cover;
    background-position:center;

    min-height:100vh;
    color:white;

}


/* HERO */

.hero{

    min-height:100vh;

    display:flex;

    flex-direction:column;

    justify-content:center;

    align-items:center;

    text-align:center;

    padding:40px;

    overflow:hidden;

}


.logo{

    font-size:4rem;

    font-weight:900;

    letter-spacing:8px;

    color:white;

}


.logo span{

    color:var(--gold);

}



.tagline{

    margin-top:20px;

    font-size:1.5rem;

    letter-spacing:3px;

}



/* HANGAR DOORS */

.hangar{

    margin:50px auto;

    width:80%;

    max-width:900px;

    height:250px;

    background:

    linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        #333,
        #111,
        #333
    );

    border:4px solid #555;

    display:flex;

    justify-content:center;

    align-items:center;

    position:relative;

    overflow:hidden;

}


.door{

    position:absolute;

    width:50%;

    height:100%;

    background:

    repeating-linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        #222,
        #444 20px,
        #222 40px
    );

    transition:2s;

}


.left{

    left:0;

}



.right{

    right:0;

}


.hangar:hover .left{

    transform:translateX(-100%);

}


.hangar:hover .right{

    transform:translateX(100%);

}



.car{

    font-size:80px;

    z-index:2;

}


/* CONTENT */


.card{

    max-width:800px;

    background:

    rgba(0,0,0,.75);

    padding:40px;

    border-radius:15px;

    border:1px solid #555;

}



h2{

    color:var(--gold);

    margin-bottom:20px;

}



p{

    line-height:1.7;

    margin-bottom:20px;

}




input{

    width:100%;

    padding:15px;

    margin:8px 0;

    border-radius:8px;

    border:none;

}




button{

    width:100%;

    padding:15px;

    margin-top:15px;

    background:var(--gold);

    border:none;

    border-radius:8px;

    font-weight:bold;

    cursor:pointer;

}



button:hover{

    background:white;

}



.footer{

    margin-top:30px;

    opacity:.7;

}


</style>

</head>


<body>


<section class="hero">


<div class="logo">

HANGAR <span>13</span>

</div>


<div class="tagline">

DIAGNOSE • REPAIR • MAINTAIN

</div>



<div class="hangar">

<div class="door left"></div>

<div class="door right"></div>


<div class="car">

🚘

</div>


</div>




<div class="card">


<h2>
The Future of Automotive Service Is Opening Soon
</h2>


<p>

Hangar 13 Services is building a premium automotive service platform designed around professional technicians, transparent repairs, and an exceptional customer experience.

</p>


<p>

We are currently accepting founding customers and subscription members while we secure initial business backing and expand our facility operations.

</p>


<h2>
Founding Customer Membership
</h2>


<p>

Become part of the Hangar 13 launch community.

Members receive:

<br><br>

✓ Priority scheduling

<br>

✓ Digital vehicle history

<br>

✓ Maintenance reminders

<br>

✓ Exclusive founding member pricing

<br>

✓ Early access to future services

</p>



<form>


<input 
type="text"
placeholder="Full Name"
>


<input 
type="email"
placeholder="Email Address"
>


<input 
type="tel"
placeholder="Phone Number"
>


<input 
type="text"
placeholder="Vehicle Year / Make / Model"
>


<button>

JOIN HANGAR 13

</button>


</form>



</div>



<div class="footer">

© Hangar 13 Services | Diagnose • Repair • Maintain

</div>



</section>



</body>

</html>
